vehicles.name: Mercedes-Benz C-Class
vehicles.description: A luxurious and comfortable sedan, perfect for both city driving and long trips. This C-Class comes with a premium interior, advanced safety features, and a smooth automatic transmission. It has been well-maintained and is in excellent condition, offering a great combination of style and performance.

vehicles.name: BMW 3 Series
vehicles.description: A sporty and dynamic sedan that delivers an exhilarating driving experience. This 3 Series features a powerful petrol engine, responsive handling, and a sleek design. It's a great choice for those who value performance and style. The car has a clean record and is ready for a new owner.

vehicles.name: Audi A4
vehicles.description: A sophisticated and elegant sedan with a high-quality interior and a comfortable ride. This A4 is equipped with a fuel-efficient diesel engine and the latest technology. It's a perfect family car, offering both safety and comfort. The mileage is low for its age.

vehicles.name: Ford Focus
vehicles.description: A reliable and practical hatchback with a manual transmission, making it fun to drive. This Focus is known for its excellent handling and fuel efficiency. It's a great all-rounder, perfect for daily commutes and weekend getaways. The car has been regularly serviced.

vehicles.name: Toyota Corolla
vehicles.description: A world-renowned sedan for its reliability and fuel efficiency. This Corolla is a hybrid model, offering excellent mileage and a smooth, quiet ride. It's packed with safety features and is a very practical choice for a family car. The car is in pristine condition.

vehicles.name: Volkswagen Golf
vehicles.description: A versatile and popular hatchback, the Golf offers a comfortable ride and a high-quality interior. This model is equipped with a fuel-efficient diesel engine and a manual transmission, providing an engaging driving experience. It's a great choice for those seeking a reliable and stylish car.

vehicles.name: Renault Clio
vehicles.description: A stylish and modern supermini, the Clio is perfect for city driving. It's fuel-efficient, easy to park, and comes with a range of modern features. This particular car has been well-cared-for and is in excellent condition, making it a great first car or a reliable city runabout.

vehicles.name: Skoda Octavia
vehicles.description: A spacious and practical family car, the Octavia offers exceptional value for money. It has a huge boot, a comfortable interior, and a range of clever features. This model comes with a smooth automatic gearbox and an economical diesel engine, making it ideal for long journeys.

vehicles.name: Fiat Ducato
vehicles.description: A reliable and versatile van, the Ducato is perfect for a wide range of business needs. It has a large cargo area, a robust diesel engine, and a comfortable cabin. This van has been used for light commercial work and has been regularly maintained, ensuring it's ready for any job.

vehicles.name: Mercedes-Benz Sprinter
vehicles.description: A premium and highly capable van, the Sprinter offers a comfortable driving experience and a high-quality interior. This model comes with an automatic gearbox and a powerful diesel engine, making it ideal for long-distance deliveries. It's in excellent condition and has a full service history.

vehicles.name: Honda CBR
vehicles.description: A legendary supersport motorcycle, the CBR offers incredible performance and sharp handling. This bike is in pristine condition with low mileage and has been fitted with some tasteful aftermarket parts. It's a perfect choice for track days or spirited weekend rides. Not for the faint-hearted!

vehicles.name: Yamaha MT-07
vehicles.description: A hugely popular naked bike, the MT-07 is known for its punchy engine and agile handling. It's a versatile motorcycle that's great for both commuting and having fun on twisty roads. This bike is in excellent condition and has been well-maintained, making it a great choice for riders of all levels.

vehicles.name: Mercedes-Benz E-Class
vehicles.description: The E-Class is the epitome of comfort and sophistication. This executive sedan is packed with technology and safety features, making every journey a pleasure. With its efficient diesel engine and smooth automatic transmission, it's the perfect car for business or pleasure. It has a full service history.

vehicles.name: BMW 5 Series
vehicles.description: A premium executive sedan that perfectly blends performance and luxury. The 5 Series offers a dynamic driving experience, a spacious and comfortable interior, and a host of advanced features. This car is in immaculate condition and has been meticulously maintained. A true driver's car.

vehicles.name: Audi A6
vehicles.description: A technologically advanced and beautifully crafted executive sedan. The A6 boasts a stunning interior with a dual-touchscreen infotainment system and a smooth, refined ride. This low-mileage example is in as-new condition and represents a great opportunity to own a premium German car.

vehicles.name: Ford Mondeo
vehicles.description: A spacious and comfortable family car that's also great to drive. The Mondeo offers a refined ride, a well-equipped interior, and a large boot. This model has a punchy petrol engine and a slick manual gearbox, making it a pleasure to drive on any road. It has a full service history.

vehicles.name: Toyota Camry
vehicles.description: A large and comfortable hybrid sedan that's incredibly fuel-efficient. The Camry is known for its reliability and low running costs, making it a smart choice for families and long-distance drivers. This car is in excellent condition and has been well-looked-after. A very sensible purchase.

vehicles.name: Volkswagen Passat
vehicles.description: A comfortable and refined family car with a premium feel. The Passat offers a spacious interior, a large boot, and a smooth ride. This model has a frugal diesel engine and a manual gearbox, making it an economical choice for high-mileage drivers. It's in great condition for its age.

vehicles.name: Renault Megane
vehicles.description: A stylish and distinctive family hatchback with a comfortable ride and a well-equipped interior. The Megane stands out from the crowd with its bold design and C-shaped headlights. This car has a punchy petrol engine and a manual gearbox, making it a fun and engaging car to drive.

vehicles.name: Skoda Superb
vehicles.description: An incredibly spacious and comfortable family car that rivals premium models for refinement. The Superb has a vast amount of legroom in the back and a huge boot, making it the perfect car for growing families. This model has a powerful diesel engine and a smooth automatic gearbox.

vehicles.name: Fiat Doblo
vehicles.description: A practical and versatile van that's perfect for small businesses. The Doblo has a spacious cargo area and a range of clever features to make your working day easier. This van has a reliable diesel engine and a manual gearbox, and it has been well-maintained by its previous owner.

vehicles.name: Opel Vivaro
vehicles.description: A popular and reliable medium-sized van, the Vivaro is a great choice for a wide range of trades. It has a comfortable cabin, a large and practical load area, and a fuel-efficient diesel engine. This van is in excellent condition and is ready to be put to work.

vehicles.name: Suzuki V-Strom
vehicles.description: A versatile adventure bike that's as happy on the road as it is on the trail. The V-Strom is known for its comfortable riding position, reliable engine, and go-anywhere ability. This bike has been well-looked-after and comes with a range of useful accessories. Ready for your next adventure!

vehicles.name: Ducati Panigale
vehicles.description: A stunningly beautiful and incredibly fast supersport motorcycle. The Panigale is a masterpiece of Italian engineering, offering breathtaking performance and razor-sharp handling. This bike is in immaculate condition and is a true collector's item. Not for the inexperienced rider!

vehicles.name: Mercedes-Benz S-Class
vehicles.description: The S-Class is the pinnacle of luxury motoring. This flagship sedan is packed with the latest technology and offers an unparalleled level of comfort and refinement. With its powerful diesel engine and air suspension, it glides over any road surface. The ultimate luxury car experience.

vehicles.name: BMW X5
vehicles.description: A large and luxurious SUV that's also great to drive. The X5 offers a commanding driving position, a spacious and high-quality interior, and powerful performance. This car is in excellent condition and has a full BMW service history. The perfect car for families who don't want to compromise on style or performance.

vehicles.name: Audi Q7
vehicles.description: A luxurious and practical seven-seat SUV with a beautifully crafted interior. The Q7 is packed with technology and offers a comfortable and refined ride. This model has a powerful diesel engine and Audi's legendary Quattro all-wheel-drive system, making it a safe and capable family car in all conditions.

vehicles.name: Ford Fiesta
vehicles.description: A fun-to-drive and stylish supermini that's perfect for zipping around town. The Fiesta is known for its sharp handling and fuel-efficient EcoBoost engine. This low-mileage example is in fantastic condition and comes with a range of modern features. A great choice for a first car.

vehicles.name: Toyota RAV4
vehicles.description: A popular and reliable hybrid SUV that's perfect for families. The RAV4 offers a spacious interior, a comfortable ride, and excellent fuel economy. This nearly-new example is in immaculate condition and comes with the balance of the manufacturer's warranty. A very smart and sensible choice.

vehicles.name: Volkswagen Tiguan
vehicles.description: A stylish and practical family SUV with a premium feel. The Tiguan offers a comfortable and spacious interior, a large boot, and a range of advanced safety features. This model has a frugal diesel engine and a smooth automatic gearbox, making it a great all-rounder. It's in excellent condition.

vehicles.name: Renault Captur
vehicles.description: A stylish and practical small SUV with a distinctive two-tone paint job. The Captur has a spacious and versatile interior with a sliding rear bench seat, making it perfect for young families. This nearly-new car has a punchy petrol engine and a manual gearbox. A great-looking and practical car.

vehicles.name: Skoda Kodiaq
vehicles.description: A large and practical seven-seat SUV that's perfect for big families. The Kodiaq is packed with clever features and offers a comfortable and refined ride. This model has a powerful diesel engine and a smooth automatic gearbox, making it a great car for long journeys. It's in excellent condition.

vehicles.name: Iveco Daily
vehicles.description: A heavy-duty and reliable van that's built to last. The Iveco Daily is a tough and capable workhorse with a large payload capacity and a powerful diesel engine. This van has been well-maintained and is ready to tackle any job you can throw at it. A great choice for demanding commercial use.

vehicles.name: Renault Master
vehicles.description: A large and practical van with a comfortable and well-equipped cabin. The Renault Master is a popular choice for a wide range of businesses, thanks to its versatility and low running costs. This van is in great condition and has a full service history. A reliable and cost-effective workhorse.

vehicles.name: KTM Duke
vehicles.description: A lightweight and agile naked bike that's perfect for carving up city streets. The KTM Duke is known for its sharp handling and punchy single-cylinder engine. This low-mileage bike is in immaculate condition and is a huge amount of fun to ride. A great choice for new riders.

vehicles.name: Ducati Monster
vehicles.description: An iconic naked bike with a rich heritage. The Ducati Monster is a stylish and charismatic motorcycle with a powerful V-twin engine and a trellis frame. This bike is in excellent condition and has been tastefully modified with some high-quality accessories. A true Italian classic.

vehicles.name: Mercedes-Benz Vito
vehicles.description: A premium and versatile medium-sized van that's perfect for a wide range of applications. The Vito offers a comfortable and car-like driving experience, a high-quality interior, and a range of advanced safety features. This van is in excellent condition and has a full service history.

vehicles.name: BMW X3
vehicles.description: A sporty and luxurious compact SUV that's great to drive. The X3 offers a perfect balance of performance, comfort, and practicality. This car is in immaculate condition and has a full BMW service history. A great choice for those who want a premium SUV that's also fun to drive.

vehicles.name: Audi Q5
vehicles.description: A comfortable and refined premium SUV with a beautifully crafted interior. The Q5 is packed with technology and offers a smooth and quiet ride. This low-mileage example is in as-new condition and comes with the balance of the manufacturer's warranty. A very desirable and capable family car.

vehicles.name: Ford Kuga

This car has a punchy petrol engine and a manual gearbox, making it a fun and engaging car to drive. It's in excellent condition.
